---
import SectionTitle from '../ui/SectionTitle.astro';
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <SectionTitle
      title="단계별 완벽 로드맵"
      subtitle="커리큘럼"
    />
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-brand uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Elementary</p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">초등부</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">사고력 확장 및 자기주도 학습 습관 형성. 상위권으로 도약할 기초 체력을 다집니다.</p>
        <a href="/curriculum" class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 font-semibold hover:text-brand transition-colors">자세히 보기 →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-brand uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Middle School</p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">중등부</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">내신 고득점 및 고등 과정 선행. 고등 입시의 핵심 격차를 미리 벌려놓습니다.</p>
        <a href="/curriculum" class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 font-semibold hover:text-brand transition-colors">자세히 보기 →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-brand uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">High School</p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">고등부</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">수능 실전 대비 및 명문대 합격 전략. 약점 보완으로 최종 목표를 달성합니다.</p>
        <a href="/curriculum" class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 font-semibold hover:text-brand transition-colors">자세히 보기 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
